# ATLAS Models Directory

This directory contains TypeScript interfaces and enums for ATLAS data models.

Models to be implemented:
- common.model.ts - Shared models (PaginationMetadata, PagedResult, ProblemDetails)
- deployment.model.ts - Deployment-related models and enums
- ai-analysis.model.ts - AI analysis, risk assessment, recommendation models
- approval.model.ts - Approval workflow models
- exception.model.ts - Exception request models
- agent.model.ts - Agent metadata, configuration, execution models
- query-builder.model.ts - Query builder models

All models are based on the ATLAS API OpenAPI specification.
